#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:1
msgid "Native CLI Quickstart"
msgstr "原生 CLI 快速开始"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:3
msgid "This quickstart shows a simple but proper MoonBit CLI layout:"
msgstr "本快速开始展示了一个简单但规范的 MoonBit CLI 布局："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:5
msgid "keep argument parsing and business logic in a library package"
msgstr "将参数解析和业务逻辑放在库包中"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:6
msgid "keep `cmd/main` small"
msgstr "保持 `cmd/main` 简洁"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:7
msgid "use `moonbitlang/async` for native IO"
msgstr "使用 `moonbitlang/async` 处理原生 IO"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:8
msgid "test the pure parts without touching the network"
msgstr "在不接触网络的情况下测试纯逻辑部分"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:10
msgid ""
"This example uses `moonbitlang/async`, which currently supports the "
"native backend best."
msgstr "这个示例使用 `moonbitlang/async`，它目前对 native 后端支持最好。"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:12
msgid "Create the project"
msgstr "创建项目"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:14
msgid "Start with a normal MoonBit module:"
msgstr "先从一个普通的 MoonBit 模块开始："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:16
msgid ""
"moon new download_cli\n"
"cd download_cli\n"
"moon add moonbitlang/async\n"
msgstr ""
"moon new download_cli\n"
"cd download_cli\n"
"moon add moonbitlang/async\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:22
msgid ""
"`argparse` is already part of the standard library, so this quickstart "
"only adds `moonbitlang/async`."
msgstr "`argparse` 已经属于标准库，因此这个快速开始只需要添加 `moonbitlang/async`。"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:24
msgid ""
"Set the preferred target to native in `moon.mod.json` so `moon run` and "
"`moon build` default to the backend that `moonbitlang/async` supports "
"best:"
msgstr ""
"在 `moon.mod.json` 中把首选目标设置为 native，这样 `moon run` 和 `moon build` 默认就会使用 "
"`moonbitlang/async` 支持最好的后端："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:26
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"name\": \"username/download_cli\",\n"
"  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n"
"  \"deps\": {\n"
"    \"moonbitlang/async\": \"0.16.6\"\n"
"  },\n"
"  \"preferred-target\": \"native\"\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"  \"name\": \"username/download_cli\",\n"
"  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n"
"  \"deps\": {\n"
"    \"moonbitlang/async\": \"0.16.6\"\n"
"  },\n"
"  \"preferred-target\": \"native\"\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:37
msgid "The final layout will look like this:"
msgstr "最终目录结构如下："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:39
msgid ""
"download_cli\n"
"├── cmd\n"
"│   └── main\n"
"│       ├── main.mbt\n"
"│       └── moon.pkg\n"
"├── cli_test.mbt\n"
"├── config.mbt\n"
"├── download.mbt\n"
"├── moon.mod.json\n"
"└── moon.pkg\n"
msgstr ""
"download_cli\n"
"├── cmd\n"
"│   └── main\n"
"│       ├── main.mbt\n"
"│       └── moon.pkg\n"
"├── cli_test.mbt\n"
"├── config.mbt\n"
"├── download.mbt\n"
"├── moon.mod.json\n"
"└── moon.pkg\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:52
msgid "Keep parsing in the library package"
msgstr "在库包中保留解析逻辑"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:54
msgid ""
"The root package defines the CLI contract. It owns the command shape and "
"turns argv into a typed config value:"
msgstr "根包定义 CLI 契约。它负责命令的形状，并把 argv 转成带类型的配置值："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:56
msgid ""
"pub struct Config {\n"
"  url : String\n"
"  output : String?\n"
"} derive(Show, Eq)\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn command() -> @argparse.Command {\n"
"  @argparse.Command::new(\n"
"    \"moon-fetch\",\n"
"    about=\"Download a URL to stdout or a file\",\n"
"    options=[\n"
"      @argparse.OptionArg::new(\n"
"        \"output\",\n"
"        short='o',\n"
"        about=\"Write the response body to this file\",\n"
"      ),\n"
"    ],\n"
"    positionals=[\n"
"      @argparse.PositionArg::new(\"url\", about=\"HTTP or HTTPS URL to "
"download\"),\n"
"    ],\n"
"  )\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn parse_config(argv : Array[String]) -> Config raise {\n"
"  let matches = @argparse.parse(command(), argv~)\n"
"  let values : Map[String, Array[String]] = matches.values\n"
"  guard values is { \"url\": [url, ..], \"output\"? : output_paths, .. } "
"else {\n"
"    fail(\"missing url\")\n"
"  }\n"
"  let output = match output_paths {\n"
"    Some([output, ..]) => Some(output)\n"
"    _ => None\n"
"  }\n"
"  { url, output }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"pub struct Config {\n"
"  url : String\n"
"  output : String?\n"
"} derive(Show, Eq)\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn command() -> @argparse.Command {\n"
"  @argparse.Command::new(\n"
"    \"moon-fetch\",\n"
"    about=\"Download a URL to stdout or a file\",\n"
"    options=[\n"
"      @argparse.OptionArg::new(\n"
"        \"output\",\n"
"        short='o',\n"
"        about=\"Write the response body to this file\",\n"
"      ),\n"
"    ],\n"
"    positionals=[\n"
"      @argparse.PositionArg::new(\"url\", about=\"HTTP or HTTPS URL to download\"),\n"
"    ],\n"
"  )\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub fn parse_config(argv : Array[String]) -> Config raise {\n"
"  let matches = @argparse.parse(command(), argv~)\n"
"  let values : Map[String, Array[String]] = matches.values\n"
"  guard values is { \"url\": [url, ..], \"output\"? : output_paths, .. } else {\n"
"    fail(\"missing url\")\n"
"  }\n"
"  let output = match output_paths {\n"
"    Some([output, ..]) => Some(output)\n"
"    _ => None\n"
"  }\n"
"  { url, output }\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:62
msgid ""
"The package descriptor imports `argparse` from `moonbitlang/core` and the"
" async libraries used by the implementation:"
msgstr "包描述文件从 `moonbitlang/core` 导入 `argparse`，并导入实现中使用的异步库："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:64
msgid ""
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/core/argparse\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async/fs\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async/http\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async/stdio\",\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/core/argparse\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async/fs\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async/http\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async/stdio\",\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:68
msgid "Put async IO behind one function"
msgstr "把异步 IO 收拢到一个函数中"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:70
msgid ""
"`run` performs the actual download. If `-o` is passed, it streams the "
"body into a file. Otherwise it writes directly to stdout:"
msgstr "`run` 负责实际下载。传入 `-o` 时，它会把响应体写入文件；否则直接写到标准输出："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:72
msgid ""
"pub async fn run(config : Config) -> Unit {\n"
"  let (response, body) = @http.get_stream(config.url)\n"
"  defer body.close()\n"
"\n"
"  guard response.code is (200..<300) else {\n"
"    fail(\"download failed: \\{response.code} \\{response.reason}\")\n"
"  }\n"
"\n"
"  match config.output {\n"
"    Some(path) => {\n"
"      let file = @fs.create(path, permission=0o644)\n"
"      defer file.close()\n"
"      file.write_reader(body)\n"
"      @stdio.stderr.write(\"saved \\{config.url} to \\{path}\\n\")\n"
"    }\n"
"    None => @stdio.stdout.write_reader(body)\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"pub async fn run(config : Config) -> Unit {\n"
"  let (response, body) = @http.get_stream(config.url)\n"
"  defer body.close()\n"
"\n"
"  guard response.code is (200..<300) else {\n"
"    fail(\"download failed: \\{response.code} \\{response.reason}\")\n"
"  }\n"
"\n"
"  match config.output {\n"
"    Some(path) => {\n"
"      let file = @fs.create(path, permission=0o644)\n"
"      defer file.close()\n"
"      file.write_reader(body)\n"
"      @stdio.stderr.write(\"saved \\{config.url} to \\{path}\\n\")\n"
"    }\n"
"    None => @stdio.stdout.write_reader(body)\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:78
msgid "Keep `main` thin"
msgstr "保持 `main` 精简"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:80
msgid ""
"`cmd/main` should usually do only wiring: read argv, build config, and "
"call the library entrypoint."
msgstr "`cmd/main` 通常只负责接线：读取 argv、构造配置并调用库入口点。"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:82
msgid ""
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbit-community/cli-quickstart-doc\" @app,\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/core/env\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async\",\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"options(\n"
"  \"is-main\": true,\n"
")\n"
msgstr ""
"import {\n"
"  \"moonbit-community/cli-quickstart-doc\" @app,\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/core/env\",\n"
"  \"moonbitlang/async\",\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"options(\n"
"  \"is-main\": true,\n"
")\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:86
msgid ""
"async fn main {\n"
"  let config = @app.parse_config(@env.args())\n"
"  @app.run(config)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"async fn main {\n"
"  let config = @app.parse_config(@env.args())\n"
"  @app.run(config)\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:92
msgid "Run the command"
msgstr "运行命令"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:94
msgid "Write the response body to stdout:"
msgstr "将响应体写到标准输出："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:96
msgid "moon run cmd/main https://example.com/feed.xml\n"
msgstr "moon run cmd/main https://example.com/feed.xml\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:100
msgid "Write it to a file:"
msgstr "将其写入文件："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:102
msgid "moon run cmd/main https://example.com/feed.xml -o feed.xml\n"
msgstr "moon run cmd/main https://example.com/feed.xml -o feed.xml\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:106
msgid "Build a native binary:"
msgstr "构建原生二进制："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:108
msgid "moon build --target native\n"
msgstr "moon build --target native\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:112
msgid "Test the pure part"
msgstr "测试纯逻辑部分"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:114
msgid ""
"The parser and config shaping logic stay easy to test because they do not"
" perform IO:"
msgstr "解析器和配置整理逻辑不执行 IO，因此仍然很容易测试："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:116
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test \"parse config for stdout\" {\n"
"  let config = parse_config([\"https://example.com/feed.xml\"])\n"
"  assert_eq(config.url, \"https://example.com/feed.xml\")\n"
"  assert_eq(config.output, None)\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test \"parse config for file output\" {\n"
"  let config = parse_config([\"https://example.com/feed.xml\", \"-o\", "
"\"feed.xml\"])\n"
"  assert_eq(config.url, \"https://example.com/feed.xml\")\n"
"  guard config.output is Some(path) else { fail(\"expected an output "
"path\") }\n"
"  assert_eq(path, \"feed.xml\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"///|\n"
"test \"parse config for stdout\" {\n"
"  let config = parse_config([\"https://example.com/feed.xml\"])\n"
"  assert_eq(config.url, \"https://example.com/feed.xml\")\n"
"  assert_eq(config.output, None)\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test \"parse config for file output\" {\n"
"  let config = parse_config([\"https://example.com/feed.xml\", \"-o\", \"feed.xml\"])\n"
"  assert_eq(config.url, \"https://example.com/feed.xml\")\n"
"  guard config.output is Some(path) else { fail(\"expected an output path\") }\n"
"  assert_eq(path, \"feed.xml\")\n"
"}\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:120
msgid "Run the tests with:"
msgstr "用下面的命令运行测试："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:122
msgid "moon test\n"
msgstr "moon test\n"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:126
msgid "When the CLI grows, keep following the same split:"
msgstr "当 CLI 继续增长时，仍然沿用同样的拆分方式："

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:128
msgid "parse and validate inputs in the library package"
msgstr "在库包中解析并校验输入"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:129
msgid "keep side effects in a small number of async functions"
msgstr "把副作用集中在少量 async 函数中"

#: ../../tutorial/cli-quickstart.md:130
msgid "keep `cmd/main` focused on wiring"
msgstr "让 `cmd/main` 专注于接线"
